!iflang [english]

!begin_node Cookie, SSND

Petra

PETRA installs a cookie (SSND) which is used by PAULA to tell PETRA
what to play with which samplefrequency.

PETRA changes some vectores using XBRA. The identification used is
SSND.

PETRA uses Timer A to do the sample output. The keyboard interrupt
routine is changed to allow sample outputs while the mouse is moved.

Keyclick & Bell are possible, but PETRA turns them off. Use the
control panel to turn them on again.

!end_node

